(6, 'Curriculum Vitae', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt&quot;&gt;Stuart James Burleigh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;7 Cheshire Ave, Birtley, Chester–le Street DH3 2BA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Tel:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt; 0191 410 3868 &amp;nbsp; | &amp;nbsp; &lt;b&gt;Mobile: &lt;/b&gt;07958 47 17 15 &amp;nbsp; | &amp;nbsp; &lt;b&gt;E-mail:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;,serif; color: blue; text-decoration: underline; text-underline: single&quot; href=&quot;mailto:plasterperfect@hotmail.co.uk&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;plasterperfect@hotmail.co.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Personal Details&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Born 21&lt;sup&gt;st&lt;/sup&gt; August 1979. Married family man. British. Full, clean driving licence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Profile: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;An innovative, enthusiastic, customer focussed professional with experience of dealing with a wide variety of people.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Background: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;On leaving school I decided to defer&lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt;my\r\nUniversity place in&lt;b&gt; &lt;/b&gt;favour of gaining work/life experience and was\r\nfortunate to be able to spend time travelling to different countries. I worked\r\nin a variety of positions but mainly as a Business Development Manager where I\r\nutilised my excellent communication and sales skills to gain valuable experience\r\nin developing relationships and overcoming social and cultural differences. On\r\nreturning to the UK I was able to extend and develop my customer service skills\r\nfirstly within the telephone based and technical support culture of Sage UK Ltd\r\nand then from becoming self-employed and running my own business dealing\r\nface-to-face with customers. I have continued to challenge myself and have\r\nachieved success in several plastering courses along with an NVQ level 3 in\r\nSolid Plastering. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;In 6 years of running my own business I have developed some excellent working\r\nrelationships with people and companies in related disciplines and am therefore\r\nalso a Sovereign Chemicals Approved Contractor for Damp proofing, timber\r\ntreatment &amp;amp; cellar tanking and have been called upon as a trusted contractor for\r\nvarious local and regional firms and as a Manager to organise several\r\nindependent contractors to deliver effectively on various projects for\r\ncustomers. I work to my strengths, with an eye for detail, excellent\r\ncommunication and customer service skills, along with strong planning and\r\norganisational focus in order to achieve maximum satisfaction for my customers.\r\nI deliver to the customers and my own high quality standards and therefore\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;achieve a high level of repeat work and work through recommendations. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Career Summary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Plaster Perfect Jan 04 – Present&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Self Employed Plasterer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Responsible for all aspects of day to day running of the business &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 54.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Symbol&quot;&gt;·&lt;span style=&quot;font:7.0pt &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Work management – All job requirements fully discussed, detailed and\r\nagreed with the customer. Detailed quotations and appropriate scheduling\r\narranged in order to complete the work to a high standard on time and to budget.\r\nThe initial quotation visit allows me to understand the customer requirements,\r\nset expectations with the customer by explaining the value and high standards of\r\nthe work I will produce, and ensures I give the best first impressions in the\r\nearly stage in the relationship. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 54.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Relationship development – Due to the variety of the jobs I undertake,\r\nfrom domestic home repairs to sub-contracting for various companies, this means\r\nthat I have the opportunity to build excellent working relationships with a \r\nvariety of people from all different backgrounds &amp;amp; professions. I have excellent \r\ninfluencing and communication skills which help me develop successful \r\nprofessional relationships with all parties concerned. By ensuring I keep good \r\nworking relationships this has the added benefit of helping the jobs to run \r\nsmoothly and efficiently and often leads to recommendations and repeat work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 54.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Symbol&quot;&gt;·&lt;span style=&quot;font:7.0pt &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;My time management skills are excellent; work schedules must be\r\neffectively controlled and maintained in order to ensure the most profitable\r\noutcome from each job, with the least amount of down time between jobs but with\r\nenough contingency to ensure any overrun can be absorbed into the working week\r\nwithout impact on later jobs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 54.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Symbol&quot;&gt;·&lt;span style=&quot;font:7.0pt &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;My approach is flexible and accommodating, I often work extra hours in\r\nthe day, evenings and weekends in order to get the work ahead of any competition\r\nand to complete work at the customer’s convenience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 54.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Symbol&quot;&gt;·&lt;span style=&quot;font:7.0pt &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;I maintain and process my own accounts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.0pt; margin-left: 54.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Symbol&quot;&gt;·&lt;span style=&quot;font:7.0pt &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;I investigate, purchase and measure the success of any company\r\nadvertising undertaken.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;RTP Construction&amp;nbsp; Aug 03 – Jan 04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Ground worker, General Labourer, Plasterer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Work varied from day to day depending on company requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Transporting employees and equipment between various sites.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;General ground works – installing drainage, electric, water and BT cables to new build homes. Concreting floors, laying tarmac driveways and flag stones.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;General maintenance duties – keeping the work area, work vehicles and any storage facilities clean &amp;amp; tidy and to health and safety standards.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Plastering work – Boarding, skimming, rendering, patching.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Sage UK Ltd&amp;nbsp;Sept 01 – Aug 03&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Technical Support Advisor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Sage is a locally grown\r\nsoftware house with a Global reputation for providing quality business software\r\nand services.&amp;nbsp; This was a customer facing role with high levels of communication\r\nskills, specialist knowledge of business software and payroll practices used to\r\nsupport end users, business partners and accountants.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Communicating with customers and using\r\n	problem solving techniques to identify their query/issue with the software\r\n	and then manage them through the process to successful resolution, achieving\r\n	excellent customer satisfaction ratings&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Helping them develop their general\r\n	understanding of the functionality of the software. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Coaching customers on how to design their\r\n	required reports for payroll within the software so that month end / year\r\n	end procedures are easier due to instant access to the necessary\r\n	information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Meeting and exceeding Key Performance\r\n	Indicators set for the support teams. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Maintaining customer records and ensuring a\r\n	continuous record of the customer experience for future reference, and also\r\n	to identify any recurring issues within the product to highlight for further\r\n	development/improvement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Customer needs assessment for any further\r\n	offerings to benefit them, for example additional product training.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Development of comprehensive computer skills\r\n	to support the customer, maintain business records and ensure customer\r\n	communications via e-mail, mail etc were detailed, thorough and\r\n	professional; Proficient in Microsoft Word, Excel, Outlook and Powerpoint,\r\n	along with&amp;nbsp; Sage bespoke internal systems. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Sage Direct Sales &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Working to achieve strict monthly sales and performance targets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;I worked a set list of customer accounts,\r\n	reviewing the type, size and software history of companies in order to\r\n	produce a needs assessment and identify appropriate sales opportunities for\r\n	further Sage programmes, training, stationary etc. This required awareness\r\n	of the full range of Sage products along with a general understanding of\r\n	wider business processes and requirements.&amp;nbsp; It was also imperative that I\r\n	built up a good rapport with the customers so they felt confident and\r\n	trusted in what I was selling them and how it would benefit their business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Education and Technical Skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;GCSE Maths, English, French &amp;amp; Dual Award Science.&amp;nbsp; Ryton Comprehensive School, Ryton (1995)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;Advanced GNVQ Engineering (Distinction) and A-level Technology, Emmanuel College (1998)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;NVQ Level 3 Solid plastering – Ashington College 2009&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;CSCS (Construction Skills Certification Scheme) Gold Card &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 6, 0),
